snippet: The Butler Bulldogs are the Beatles of the new-look Atlantic 10, and they got all they could handle from the Colonials before holding on for a victory.
abstract: Butler defeats George Washington, 59-56, in men's college basketball.
lead_paragraph: The Butler Bulldogs are the Beatles of the new-look Atlantic 10, and they got all they could handle from the Colonials before holding on for a victory.

headline.print_headline: Used to Being Everyone’s Big Game, Butler Survives One
headline.seo: George Washington Gives Butler Warm Welcome, Then Nearly Pulls Off Upset
headline.main: A Sellout Crowd for George Washington, but a Win for Butler
